<v Speaker 1>There are just a handful of verbs that are not verbs of movement, for example, like ir, volver

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.080
<v Speaker 1>salir that need a to connect.

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:43.680
<v Speaker 1>Apart from these, there are just a handful of verbs that use some preposition to connect.

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:48.080
<v Speaker 1>And empesar and commenç are two of them.

